SNB Sees No Deflation in Switzerland, Handelszeitung Says

-- B y   R a i n e r   B u e r g i n
-- 
2011-02-16T18:46:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-16/snb-sees-no-deflation-in-switzerland-handelszeitung-says.html
Swiss central bank President Philipp Hildebrand said the  Swiss National Bank  has guaranteed price
stability and there are no deflationary tendencies in the Alpine
country,  Handelszeitung  reported. The bank did not aim to defend
a fixed exchange rate when it acted in the foreign exchange
market, Hildebrand told the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rainer Buergin in Berlin at 
 rbuergin1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Hertling at   jhertling@bloomberg.net  